import styled from "styled-components"

const Container = styled.div`
height: 40vh;
background-color: rebeccapurple
`

const Left = styled.div`flex: 1;`
const Center = styled.div`flex: 1;`
const Right = styled.div`flex: 1;`

export const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Left>asf</Left>
            <Center>vsdav</Center>
            <Right>vdv</Right>
        </Container>
    )
}
